$4.5 Million to Preserve Languages Threatened With Extinction\"</a>. <i>National Endowment for the Humanities</i>. 2012-08-09<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2012-08-29</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=National+Endowment+for+the+Humanities&amp;rft.atitle=NEH+and+NSF+Award+%244.5+Million+to+Preserve+Languages+Threatened+With+Extinction&amp;rft.date=2012-08-09&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.neh.gov%2Fnews%2Fpress-release%2F2012-08-09&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMark+Liberman\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">\n<cite class=\"citation conference\">Steven Bird; Florian R. Hanke; Oliver Adams; Haejoong Lee (2014). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://acl2014.org/acl2014/W14-22/pdf/W14-2201.pdf\"><i>Aikuma: A Mobile App for Collaborative Language Documentation</i></a> <span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(PDF)</span>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://acl2014.org/acl2014/W14-22/index.html\">Workshop on the Use of Computational Methods in the Study of Endangered Languages</a>. Association for Computational Linguistics. pp.&#160;1\u20135<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2016-04-30</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=conference&amp;rft.btitle=Aikuma%3A+A+Mobile+App+for+Collaborative+Language+Documentation&amp;rft.pages=1-5&amp;rft.pub=Association+for+Computational+Linguistics&amp;rft.date=2014&amp;rft.au=Steven+Bird&amp;rft.au=Florian+R.+Hanke&amp;rft.au=Oliver+Adams&amp;rft.au=Haejoong+Lee&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Facl2014.org%2Facl2014%2FW14-22%2Fpdf%2FW14-2201.pdf&amp;rfr_id=i